title: Vice President Biden to Travel to Brazil | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Vice President


For Immediate Release
December 05, 2014

 



Vice President Biden to Travel to Brazil




Vice President Joe Biden will travel to Brazil to lead the U.S. Delegation to the Inauguration of Her Excellency Dilma Rousseff on January 1st. Additional details about the Vice Presidentâ€™s trip will be released at a later date.
